Title: Journey around India on bicycle
DateModified: '2019-03-03'
DatePublished: '2019-03-03'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/journey-around-india-on-bicycle
SetInCountry: India
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Surjit Kumar Sandhu
AuthorCountry: India
Text: I travel around India on bicycle 10000km in 90 days solo ride . New India theme
  to eradicate poverty, Castiesm, corruption, terrorism , communalism,and make Clean
  india , its very wonderful to travel in diversity of culture, language, food and
  dress style make interesting every pedal towards next mile. People love to met and
  help in way to know a cyclist come to visit thier city or village . They all make
  a place in my heart and my book . It was different as media reports about a society
  , they all maybe different but all only want to be happy and make surrounding beautiful
  , so know i wish to explore another country or diversity , how they deal with a
  traveler to whom will met first and last time in life , how they make place in his
  book and perception about them for all world if anyone wants to visit those book
  characters
